636
00:39:01,385 --> 00:39:03,052
Ne, rodilo se kad sam otišao.

637
00:39:03,613 --> 00:39:04,822
To je teško.

638
00:39:21,675 --> 00:39:22,802
Starks, jesi dobro?

639
00:39:23,050 --> 00:39:24,582
