640
00:39:25,287 --> 00:39:26,987
Stojim dole, Stojim dole.

641
00:39:32,772 --> 00:39:34,362
To je bilo malo preblizu.

642
00:39:35,673 --> 00:39:37,455
Starks, jesi li u redu?

643
00:39:37,863 --> 00:39:39,017
Da.

644
00:39:41,197 --> 00:39:43,017
